224
00:09:58,350 --> 00:10:00,540
which is the Clumio way.

225
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:03,960
So in the absence of Clumio,
it's an arduous process.

226
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:07,650
For each partition's last
known good point in time,

227
00:10:07,650 --> 00:10:10,590
